DESCRIPTION:Every Friday in S.F.’s historic North Beach – come to Cigar Bar LIVE Salsa Music\, Salsa lessons with Ava & Rodolfo\, delicious food and tasty drinks\nHappy Hour food & drink specials 5:30-7:30pm\nSalsa class w/ Ava & Rodolfo 7:30-8:30pm\nLIVE Salsa band 9:30pm
