SUMMARY:Sábado de Noche Tropical at La Rumba
DESCRIPTION:Make La Rumba your weekend destination for sizzling Latin nightlife! Whether you’re looking for a dance lesson\, a refreshing hand-crafted cocktail\, or Denver’s hottest mix of sultry Latin rhythms\, we’ve got you covered! \nTonight’s Happenings\n•7:00 pm Doors open\n•7:00ish pm – 8:00 pm Beginning bachata lesson\n•8:00 pm Bar opens for drinks\n•8:00 pm – 9:00 pm Beginning salsa lesson\n•9:00 pm – 1:30 am DJs \nCover*\n•$10 without dance lessons\n•$15 with dance lesson(s) \n*Cover for All Saturdays Except 2nd Saturday of Month\n• $10 without dance lessons | $15 with dance lesson(s)
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-saturdays-at-larumba/2026-03-21/
LOCATION:LaRumba\, 99 West 9th Avenue\, Denver\, CO\, 80204\, United States
CATEGORIES:Denver
