SUMMARY:Latin Fridays & Saturdays at Lula Lounge
DESCRIPTION:Weekends\, we go to Havana\, where the vibrant rhythms ignite our souls and live music\, dance lessons\, & skillful DJs make it a perfect night! \n \nArrive between 7pm and 8pm to indulge in a delectable three-course dinner and explore the Lula carefully curated bar menu\, featuring our signature tropical cocktails. The dance lesson at 9pm will ease you into the Latin groove\, preparing you for a night of dancing to the tropical rhythms of one of Lula’s world-famous live salsa orchestras\, performing two sets starting at 10pm and midnight. \nBetween live music sets\, Lula’s talented DJs keep the party going with a mix of top 40\, salsa\, bachata\, reggaeton\, and other Latin hits. Don’t miss out on this electrifying night! \nAgenda \n7:00 PM\nDoors Open for Dinner and Drinks \nArrive between 7 and 8 pm to enjoy a fabulous dinner and tropical drinks. Reservations available at lula.ca/reservations \n9:00 PM\nBeginner’s Dance Lesson \nGet ready to have some fun and break the ice with a beginners dance lesson provided some of the best dance schools in the city. (No partner necessary!) \n10:00 PM\nLive Salsa Set 1 \nToronto’s best salsa bands take to the stage and deliver irresistible tropical rhythms. Nothing compares to experiencing this music with a LIVE band! \n11:00 PM\nDJ Set 1 \nOur featured DJ will keep the party going all night with top 40\, salsa\, bachata\, reggeaton and other Latin hits. \n12:00 AM\nLive Salsa Set 2 \nToronto’s best salsa bands take to the stage and deliver some of the best tropical rhythms this side of Havana! \n1:00 AM\nDJ Set 2 \nOur featured DJ returns to keep the party going until closing with more top 40\, salsa\, bachata\, reggeaton and Latin hits.
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/latin-fridays-at-lula-lounge/2026-03-21/
LOCATION:Lula Lounge\, 1585 Dundas Street West\, Toronto\, ON\, M6K 1T9\, Canada
CATEGORIES:Toronto
END:VEVENT
